Beyond Innocence (1990)

Starring: Lauren Brice, Kristarah Knight, Tiara West, Raven Richards, Suzie Bartlett, Brittany Morgan
Categories: Classic
Date Added: 1990
(958 Mb)

Tiara and Raven Richards are the wickedly beautiful seasoned thieves out to get what they want - by any means. As luck would have it, they are caught red handed during a break-in by two female cops - played by the sultry Lauren Brice and the sensational Brittany Morgan. In the ensuing struggle, Raven manages to escape the long arm of the law and finds herself in a steamy downtown club as a temporary refuge away from her pursuers. There she meets the innocent and unsuspecting Suzie Bartlett and a diabolical plan begins to form in her mind.
